        <p style="margin-top:10px">We recommend taking advantage of the warranty rather than returning &mdash; if the camera has a functional issue within 6 months, we'll fix or replace it at no cost.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:10px;color:rgba(78,71,65,0.6);font-size:11px">To initiate a return, contact us at <a href="mailto:sx70@brooklynfilmcamera.com" style="color:inherit">sx70@brooklynfilmcamera.com</a> with your order number.</p>
